OL,3,CHospital told to make 'immediate
OL,4,Cimprovements' on maternity ward
OL,6,FA South West hospital has been told to
OL,7,Fmake "immediate improvements" to its
OL,8,Fmaternity services amid safety
OL,9,Fconcerns following a surprise
OL,10,Finspection.
OL,12,FInspectors from the Care Quality
OL,13,FCommission (CQC) visited
OL,14,FGloucestershire Royal Hospital in
OL,15,FMarch and April 2024.
OL,17,FFollowing the inspection, urgent
OL,18,Fconditions were imposed to "make
OL,19,Fimprovements ensuring the safe
OL,20,Ftreatment of women and people using
OL,21,Fthe service".
