OL,3,CHospital told to make 'immediate
OL,4,Cimprovements' on maternity ward
OL,6,FThese conditions continue to remain in
OL,7,Fplace, while maternity services at the
OL,8,Fhospital have been re-rated
OL,9,F'inadequate'.
OL,11,FCatherine Campbell, CQC's head of
OL,12,Fhospital inspection, said positive
OL,13,Fchanges have been made but "not enough
OL,14,Fwork had been done".
OL,16,FShe said: "We were still concerned
OL,17,Fabout how the trust managed systems to
OL,18,Fidentify risks to mothers, babies and
OL,19,Fpeople using the service.
