OL,3,CHospital told to make 'immediate
OL,4,Cimprovements' on maternity ward
OL,6,F"Some people told us they didn't
OL,7,Falways feel safe in the department.
OL,8,FLeaders didn't properly induct agency
OL,9,Fstaff or provide access to essential
OL,10,Fsystems, causing care delays.
OL,12,F"For example, agency midwives didn't
OL,13,Falways have security door fobs and
OL,14,Fwould need to rely on other staff
OL,15,Fduring emergencies, creating potential
OL,16,Frisks to people's safety due to those
OL,17,Fdelays.
