OL,6,FThe inspection was carried out in
OL,7,Fresponse to concerns about ambulance
OL,8,Fhandover times at the hospital's
OL,9,FAccident and Emergency department.
OL,11,FIn its report, the CQC said: "The
OL,12,Frating for urgent and emergency care
OL,13,Ffollowing this inspection remains
OL,14,Funchanged and is re-rated as requires
OL,15,Fimprovement as are the ratings for
OL,16,Feffective and responsive.
OL,18,F"Caring and well-led have been re-
OL,19,Frated as good. Safe has improved from
OL,20,Frequires improvement to good.
